Stacy J. Smith 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President, Manufacturing, Operations and Sales at INTEL CORP, Stacy J. Smith  made $7,786,900 in total compensation.  Of this total $800,000 was received as a salary, $1,912,400 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $4,611,000 was awarded as stock and $463,500 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


